<lb n="0942a14" ed="T"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="001"/><cb:jhead>佛說心明經<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942002">〔一卷〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942002" type="mod" resp="CBETA">一卷【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942002"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="T" n="0942a15"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0942a16"/><byline cb:type="Translator">西晉<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942003">月氏國三藏＝三藏法師【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月氏國三藏【大】，三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942003"><lem wit="【大】">月氏國三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb ed="T" n="0942a17"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0942a1701">聞如<note n="0942a1701" resp="CBETA" type="add">是【CB】，足【大】</note><app n="0942a1701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA">是</lem><rdg wit="【大】">足</rdg></app>：</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0942a1704">一時，佛遊王舍城靈鷲山，與五百比
<lb ed="T" n="0942a18"/>丘四部眾俱。佛以晨旦著衣持鉢，往至一縣
<lb ed="T" n="0942a19"/>而行分衛，諸天龍神追於上侍，到梵志館門
<lb ed="T" n="0942a20"/>外而<note place="foot text" n="0942004" type="orig" resp="Taisho">住＋（分衛）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942004" type="mod" resp="CBETA">住【大】，住分衛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942004"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">住分衛</rdg></app>，佛放大光普炤十方。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0942a2012" rend="inline">時梵志婦執
<lb n="0942a21" ed="T"/>爨炊飯，見光照身，身得安隱，解<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942005" place="foot text">悍＝懌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942005" type="mod" resp="CBETA">悍【大】，懌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942005"><lem wit="【大】">悍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">懌</rdg></app>無量，心
<lb n="0942a22" ed="T"/>自念言：「今<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942006" place="foot text">此＝比【元】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0942006">此【大】，比【元】</note><app n="0942006"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">比</rdg></app>光耀，不似日月釋梵，四王諸天
<lb n="0942a23" ed="T"/>之明，躬荷熙怡不能自勝。」還顧見佛端正<note n="0942007" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">殊＝姝【元】【明】</note><note n="0942007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殊【大】，姝【元】【明】</note><app n="0942007"><lem wit="【大】">殊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">姝</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0942a24"/>好，如星中月奇相巍巍，眾好具足諸根澹泊，
<lb ed="T" n="0942a25"/>無有衰入<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942008" place="foot text">建＝逮【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0942008">建【大】，逮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942008"><lem wit="【大】">建</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">逮</rdg></app>最上寂，得第一定，<note place="foot text" n="0942009" type="orig" resp="Taisho">如＝始【宮】</note><note n="0942009" type="mod" resp="CBETA">如【大】，始【宮】</note><app n="0942009"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">始</rdg></app>日初出
<lb ed="T" n="0942a26"/>現<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942010" place="foot text">于＝乎【宋】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0942010">于【大】，乎【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0942010"><lem wit="【大】">于</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">乎</rdg></app>山崗，如轉輪王臨幸大殿，<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942011">補＝寶【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0942011">補【大】，寶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942011"><lem wit="【大】">補</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">寶</rdg></app>臣翼從；
<lb ed="T" n="0942a27"/>又若帝釋顯據忉利，猶梵天王於第七尊，如
<lb n="0942a28" ed="T"/>高山雪<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942012">冏＋（居永反）夾註【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0942012">冏【大】，冏(居永反)【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0942012"><lem wit="【大】">冏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">冏<note place="inline">居永反</note></rdg></app>灼普現，倍加踊躍，重自<note n="0942013" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">惟忖＝忖惟【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0942013">惟忖【大】，忖惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942013"><lem wit="【大】">惟忖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">忖惟</rdg></app>：「今
<lb ed="T" n="0942a29"/>得覩佛及<note n="0942014" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">佛＝眾【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0942014">佛【大】，眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942014"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">眾</rdg></app>弟子，誠副宿願，欲以食饌奉進
<pb n="0942b" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0569.0942b"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b01"/>正覺。隱察愚夫不信道德，志<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942015" place="foot text">在＝存【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在【大】，存【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942015"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">存</rdg></app>邪疑六十
<lb ed="T" n="0942b02"/>二見，見<note place="foot text" n="0942016" type="orig" resp="Taisho">妾＝我【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942016" type="mod" resp="CBETA">妾【大】，我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942016"><lem wit="【大】">妾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">我</rdg></app>所施必興結恨。宿命愆咎失雄
<lb n="0942b03" ed="T"/>猛男，嬰墜女像羈制於人，欲施聖尊不得由
<lb n="0942b04" ed="T"/>已，宜順護意當如之何？」便即<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942017" place="foot text">箄＝捍【宋】，壓【元】【明】，捭【宮】</note><note n="0942017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">箄【大】，捍【宋】，壓【元】【明】，捭【宮】</note><app n="0942017"><lem wit="【大】">箄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">捍</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">壓</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">捭</rdg></app>飯取汁一杓
<lb ed="T" n="0942b05"/>以用上佛。佛之威神，鉢中自然有百味食，佛
<lb n="0942b06" ed="T"/>時達嚫，口歎頌曰：</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b07"/><lg rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em" xml:id="lgT14p0942b0701"><l>「假以馬百疋，</l><l>金銀挍鞍勒，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b08"/><l>用惠施於人，</l><l>不如杓飯汁；</l>
<lb n="0942b09" ed="T"/><l>設以七寶車，</l><l>載滿諸<note n="0942018" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">珍琦＝琦珍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942018" type="mod" resp="CBETA">珍琦【大】，琦珍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942018"><lem wit="【大】">珍琦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">琦珍</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0942b10" ed="T"/><l>杓飯汁施佛，</l><l>其福過於彼；</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b11"/><l>若施白象百，</l><l>明珠瓔珞飾，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b12"/><l>供佛一杓汁，</l><l>其福超彼上；</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b13"/><l>如聖轉輪王、</l><l>普賢玉女后，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b14"/><l>端正無有比，</l><l>七寶瓔珞身。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b15"/><l>如是之妙類，</l><l>其數各有百，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b16"/><l>悉以配施人，</l><l>不如一杓汁。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0942b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0942b1701">於時，梵志靜住而聽，聞佛所歎，心懷疑惑，前
<lb n="0942b18" ed="T"/>問佛言：「一杓飯汁何所直也，而乃稱讚？若干
<lb n="0942b19" ed="T"/>寶施、象馬車乘，不可<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942019" place="foot text">呰毀＝訾數【元】，言數【明】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0942019">呰毀【大】，訾數【元】，言數【明】</note><app n="0942019"><lem wit="【大】">呰毀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">訾數</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">言數</rdg></app>，而云不如杓飯汁
<lb ed="T" n="0942b20"/>施，斯之飯汁不直一錢，然乃咨嗟若干億倍，
<lb ed="T" n="0942b21"/>孰當信哉？」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0942b22"/><p xml:id="pT14p0942b2201">於是，世尊尋即顯露廣長之舌，以覆其面上
<lb ed="T" n="0942b23"/>至梵天，告梵志曰：「吾從無數億百千劫，常
<lb ed="T" n="0942b24"/>行至誠六度無極，施諸所安，有而不惜，乃獲
<lb n="0942b25" ed="T"/>斯舌，寧以妄語能致之乎？吾欲問，卿至誠答
<lb n="0942b26" ed="T"/>之。曾頗往返舍衛羅閱，中路<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942020" place="foot text">（見）＋有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942020" type="mod" resp="CBETA">有【大】，見有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942020"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">見有</rdg></app>樹名尼拘
<lb n="0942b27" ed="T"/>類，蔭庇人眾五百乘車<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942021" place="foot text">乎＝不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乎【大】，不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942021"><lem wit="【大】">乎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不</rdg></app>？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0942b2711">對曰：「唯然，有是
<lb n="0942b28" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" n="0942022" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔樹我〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0942022">樹我【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942022"><lem wit="【大】">樹，我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>所見也。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0942b2806">世尊又問：「其子大如？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0942b2814">答曰：「形
<lb n="0942b29" ed="T"/>如芥子。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0942b2904">佛告梵志：「卿真兩舌。實如芥子，樹何
<pb n="0942c" xml:id="T14.0569.0942c" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0942c01"/><note n="0942023" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">巨乎＝巨大【宋】【宮】，大乎【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0942023">巨乎【大】，巨大【宋】【宮】，大乎【元】【明】</note><app n="0942023"><lem wit="【大】">巨乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">巨大</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">大乎</rdg></app>？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0942c0103">對曰：「審爾，不敢欺也。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0942c0111" rend="inline">佛又告曰：「種如
<lb n="0942c02" ed="T"/>芥子，生樹廣大，地之生<note n="0942024" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">殖＝植【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0942024">殖【大】，植【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942024"><lem wit="【大】">殖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">植</rdg></app>適無所置、所覆彌
<lb ed="T" n="0942c03"/>廣，乃<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942025">況＝爾況復【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0942025">況【大】，爾況復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942025"><lem wit="【大】">況</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">爾況復</rdg></app>如來無上至真、等正覺，無量福會普
<lb n="0942c04" ed="T"/>勝者哉？戒、定、慧、<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942026">解脫＝脫脫【宋】【元】，解度【宮】</note><note n="0942026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">解脫【大】，脫脫【宋】【元】，解度【宮】</note><app n="0942026"><lem wit="【大】">解脫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">脫脫</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">解度</rdg></app>、<note place="foot text" n="0942027" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔解脫〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942027" type="mod" resp="CBETA">解脫【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942027"><lem wit="【大】">解脫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>知見事，大慈弘
<lb ed="T" n="0942c05"/>哀無所不濟，以饌供獻<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942028">功＝福【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">功【大】，福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942028"><lem wit="【大】">功</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">福</rdg></app>祚難計。」梵志默然
<lb ed="T" n="0942c06"/>無以加報。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0942c0605" rend="inline">時佛乃笑，五色光從口出，照十方，
<lb n="0942c07" ed="T"/>五趣之類——<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942029">天＝夫【宋】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0942029">天【大】，夫【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0942029"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">夫</rdg></app>欲<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942030">止＝至【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942030" type="mod" resp="CBETA">止【大】，至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942030"><lem wit="【大】">止</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">至</rdg></app>，人心喜，餓鬼<note n="0942031" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">飽＋（滿）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飽【大】，飽滿【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942031"><lem wit="【大】">飽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飽滿</rdg></app>，地獄
<lb n="0942c08" ed="T"/>痛息，畜生意開——罪除，尋光來詣佛所。諸佛
<lb n="0942c09" ed="T"/>笑法皆有常瑞；授菩薩決，遍照十方光從頂
<lb n="0942c10" ed="T"/>入；授緣覺莂，光入面門；授聲聞莂，光入肩斗；
<lb ed="T" n="0942c11"/>說生天事，光從䐡入；說降人中，光從膝入；說
<lb ed="T" n="0942c12"/>趣三苦，<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0942032" place="foot text">（光）＋從【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942032" type="mod" resp="CBETA">從【大】，光從【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942032"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">光從</rdg></app>足心入。諸佛之欣，不以欲笑，不
<lb n="0942c13" ed="T"/>以瞋笑，不以癡笑，不放逸笑，不利欲笑，不
<lb n="0942c14" ed="T"/>榮貴笑，不富饒笑，今佛普等愍傷群萌，行
<lb n="0942c15" ed="T"/>大慈笑無斯七也。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0942c1508" rend="inline">賢者阿難分別七法——知法、
<lb n="0942c16" ed="T"/>解義、曉時、了節、暢眾會事、<note place="foot text" n="0942033" type="orig" resp="Taisho">自＝思【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942033" type="mod" resp="CBETA">自【大】，思【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942033"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">思</rdg></app>省己身、明眾人
<lb n="0942c17" ed="T"/>根——即從座起更整衣服，長跪問佛：「佛何<note place="foot text" n="0942034" type="orig" resp="Taisho">因＋（緣）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0942034">因【大】，因緣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942034"><lem wit="【大】">因</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">因緣</rdg></app>
<lb n="0942c18" ed="T"/>笑？願說其意。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0942c1806">佛告阿難：「見梵志婦發大意乎？」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0942c19"/><p xml:id="pT14p0942c1901">對曰：「已見。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0942c1905" rend="inline">佛言：「斯婦壽終，當轉女像<note n="0942035" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">得＝後【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0942035">得【大】，後【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942035"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">後</rdg></app>為
<lb n="0942c20" ed="T"/>男子，生于天上諸天中尊，下生世間為人中
<lb n="0942c21" ed="T"/>上，解深妙法如幻如化，如水中月、影、響、野馬，
<lb ed="T" n="0942c22"/>却三十劫當得作佛，名曰心明如來、至真、等
<lb n="0942c23" ed="T"/>正覺、明行成為、善逝、世間解、無上士、道法御、天
<lb n="0942c24" ed="T"/>人師，號佛，世尊。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0942c2407" rend="inline">梵志心伏，五體投地剋心自
<lb ed="T" n="0942c25"/>責，懺曰：「我如小兒愚癡闇冥，懷疑猶豫不識
<lb ed="T" n="0942c26"/>大聖，口出麁言，唯原罪釁。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0942c2611" rend="inline">佛言：「善哉！善哉！若
<lb n="0942c27" ed="T"/>自見過，歸命於佛，於道、法、律悔殃塵者，其咎
<lb n="0942c28" ed="T"/>損<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0942036">減＝滅【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0942036">減【大】，滅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942036"><lem wit="【大】">減</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">滅</rdg></app>，福增日滋。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0942c2807" rend="inline">梵志<note place="foot text" n="0942037" type="orig" resp="Taisho">進啟＝啟進【三】【宮】</note><note n="0942037" type="mod" resp="CBETA">進啟【大】，啟進【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0942037"><lem wit="【大】">進啟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">啟進</rdg></app>：「唯垂大哀！加恩
<lb n="0942c29" ed="T"/>矜攝，令得出家。」佛即納受以為沙門，鬚髮則
<pb n="0943a" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0569.0943a"/>
<lb n="0943a01" ed="T"/>除法衣在身。於時，世尊講四聖諦——苦、<note n="0943001" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">習＝集【元】【明】</note><note n="0943001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">習【大】，集【元】【明】</note><app n="0943001"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">集</rdg></app>、盡、
<lb ed="T" n="0943a02"/>道——梵志踊躍，漏盡意解。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0943a0210" rend="inline">佛說如是，賢者阿難，
<lb ed="T" n="0943a03"/>諸四部眾，天人龍神，皆發道意，歡喜<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0943002">稽首＋（而退）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0943002">稽首【大】，稽首而退【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0943002"><lem wit="【大】">稽首</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">稽首而退</rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="T" n="0943a04"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說心明經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
